import { Card } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Footer = () => (
    <>
        <Card>
            <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px180" />
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Text>  Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk
                    of the card's content.  
                </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
    </>
)

export default Footer;
